UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Notes:: 1. **How did we connect?** 1. Raghu from PB 1. Raghu is a friend 1. He is being advised by Umang from CarDekho Group 1. Recently did the NCR visit circuit 1. **Pranil** 1. From Mumbai 1. South — suburbs — Ghatpokar — Powai now 1. GUJ middle class household 1. Dad is a trader of dry fruits & dates 1. Engineering — KJ Somaiya 1. MBA - GIM Goa 1. Citi banker for life 1. UHNI wealth mgt — ₹45 crore portfolio 1. Ratan tata family office client 1. Specialized domains across identity, fraud & risk 1. Karza 1. 0-1 journey as Product person 1. 8 member team at joining 1. 250 team at exit 1. Resp. w/ CTO to hire engineering staff of 150 1. Making 20L in revenue at entry 1. Making 85 crore in revenue at exit 1. Sold to Perfios for ₹650 crore 1. Built video KYC product + sandbox 1. Industry 1st product — reference check for onboarding new hires 1. Left a lot of money on table leaving prior to acquisition by Perfios 1. MetaMap 1. Moved to Mexico city for a bit 1. 15 member team (non-Indians; LATINO, EU etc) 1. $700K revenue in one year — self serve channel 1. Distressed sold to a global giant 1. Bureau.ID 1. Scaled x5 revenue on identity side 1. Head of Product role 1. He stumbled upon Tenacio 1. Waited for a long time — built for others; now for self 1. **Learning** 1. Perfios made Karza’s identity into a non-sexy industry 1. Identity biz is 85% GM — but lots of inbound competitors which brings the margin down 1. Karza growth rate is ~8% versus industry 20% 1. New players eating ...' WHERE id = 474 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Meeting at the founder’s home 2024-08-29: Attendees: @Anonymous, @Aakash and @Rahul Mathur 1. Conversations with Mallika were very helpful - didn''t want to let her go after 45 minutes 1. Want to speak to Shashank from TWT but he hasn''t responded as yet to their message 1. Questions they asked - How is DeVC money invested? - who from DeVC would be leading the investment? - Is any board seat required? 1. General Qs they asked - Do we give a board seat? - what are drag rights? - should we be worried about exit clauses? 1. Have asked for one day to come back on the ₹2.5 crore + ₹0.5 crore allocation 1. Advice given by team - Move as many of the items to CS as possible - Push Fireside to close DD ASAP 1. Business right now - Doing ₹70L revenue - have a single fabric right now - going to China to speak to manufacturers to source one more new fabric 1. Other observations - Adith from Zepto is a friend, he has been giving them QC search data - CoFo has a sewing machine in her room which she uses to create samples - Founders aren''t surrounded by the right mentors, these are product marketers - Choksi''s family business on husband side is precision medical equipment which is sold to all types of hospitals and clinics - they have offered to help with MedMitra
