UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Heads up note 2025-08-27T15:18:00.000+05:30 from @Rahul Mathur: Hi team, Sharing the heads-up note for our investment in [Tesora AI](https://tesora.ai/). It is an AI procurement analyst that streamlines the work of a sourcing team; starting with Hard Tech industries where qualified engineers earning $150K+ per annum are required to make calls / write emails to secure necessary components for complex systems. DeVC is investing $200K via the standard YC SAFE @ $20M Cap; this is a $3M round **Founders** 1. [Vivek R](https://www.linkedin.com/in/vivek-r-928871173/) 1. 2 YOE as PE investor at Sycamore Partners ($14b AUM) 1. 2 YOE @ McKinsey & Company 1. BRC from [Aditya Sukumar](https://www.linkedin.com/in/adithyasukumar?utm_source=share&utm_campaign=share_via&utm_content=profile&utm_medium=ios_app) (EM @ McKinsey) 1. *Top performer. Great technical skill set.* 1. *Definitely top decile compared to analysts and associates. * 1. *Would do whatever it took to get it done* 1. *Staying super late and being last one out was norm with him* 1. *Would you blindly back him: YES* 1. BA/MBA in Economics & Finance from UChicago; MBA was on full scholarship 1. [Federico G](https://www.linkedin.com/in/federico-reyes-gomez/) : 1. 3 YOE @ Kumo AI as founding engineer (fastest promotion) 1. *BRC from Viman Deb (Head of Product @ Kumo AI)* 1. *Fed is top 3 engineers in my 16 years career* 1. *Went on his own to use his extra time to be part of the solutions engineering team and going to customers. *...' WHERE id = 479 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Notes:: **Views:** Yashi: Strong Maybe (should do more work with a 2PE) **Spiky: **0 **EF/FF: **FF **Founder Archetype: **6 **FMF: **7 **Thesis: **6 + found him very close to 0.5 spiky, is commercial and thoughtful + knows what he is building well – could answer 2-3 layers of questions ? working on building speciality textiles for various use cases across industries (more B2B than B2C) – should deep dive + has executed reasonably well within the limited time: got great customer logos on board, one core selling product and an R&D person from domain + Decent traction with high margins: 0.5 Cr MRR with 2.75 Cr in written orders, 16% CM3 average ? need to take all of this keeping in mind the history of building in textiles ? would like to diligence on the defensibility of the product and how real the pipeline is **Notes:** **Team** [Mayank Tibrewala](https://www.linkedin.com/in/mayank-tibrewala-9abab817/?originalSubdomain=in) - Background: - Born and raised in Mumbai in a Marwari family - Father was former CFO at WellSpin India, now runs his own CA/auditing firm - Mother is a homemaker - Has a younger sister who is a CA and IIM Lucknow graduate, working in private equity - Education: - Studied Aerospace Engineering at IIT Kharagpur - MBA from IIM Ahmedabad - Career: - Started at Arete Advisors (consulting, acquired by Bain) - Chief of Staff at Asaan Jobs (acquired by OLX) - Led global denims business at Fashinza ($15M ARR) (1 year) [**Akash Kalra**](https://www.linkedin.com/in/ak...' WHERE id = 482 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
