UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Notes:: Ankit, Sahil - Both delhi, Modern and VV 2002 batch - Ankit – UK, CA, BNP Paribas - Sahil – IIMK **Ankit and Sahil started Dineout** - Lots of consumer insight and customers moving favored it as a booming industry - Restaurant tech platform - Supply chain management - Dineout passport - Payments - Close to 100mn users annually; 0.5bn GMV - Acquired by Swiggy – Jul 22 - Ticket size went up – earning 200rs / order Took 10% cash, rest Swiggy stocks Integrated Dineout till Dec ‘23 **Jan ’24 went into gardening** - UK wait times are 2 years – 8mn people waiting for a surgery; unofficially 13mn - Last trimester didn’t meet the doctor - Why are people not travelling to India 99% of travel comes from developing nation – Bangladesh, Africa, etc… - Agent driven - Agent network in both countries is strong – there are 6 agents involved - Hospitals themselves are holding camps, etc From Europe, people aren’t coming to India - 2019, 200k - 2023, 0.5mn people going to Eastern Europe 2 arbitrages at play - 3 year wait becomes 4 weeks - Avg private care of GBP 25k is 15k in Eastern Europe Why are people not coming to India? - Lack of trust in Indian infrastructure - 60k doctors in NHS are Indian - Lack of after care - Hospital stay is just 20% of the overall country - Guest houses have sprung up for these - 1-2k where attendant runs around - Or 5 star which is expensive and no after care - What if there’s an issue in case something goes wrong after I come back - Problem is the UK doct...' WHERE id = 485 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
